<item>
            <title>[LU-3741] SLES11SP2 server,Failure on test suite sanityn test_16</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3741</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/10fb6bd4-00c4-11e3-b06c-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/10fb6bd4-00c4-11e3-b06c-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_16 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;test_16 returned 1&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanityn 16&lt;/p&gt;</description>
